                     <interp inst="t18120916-214-person1675" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             - A. Ninety-nine pounds thirteen shillings.</p>
               <p>Q. Do you know what business James Folkard was - A. He was shopman to his brother, 
               <persName id="t18120916-214-person1676">
                  John 
