                     <interp inst="t18120916-214-person1680" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . Q. At the time of this commission you were a creditor - A. Yes, to 
               <persName id="t18120916-214-person1681">
                  John 
                  Folkard
               <interp inst="t18120916-214-person1681" type="surname" value="Folkard"></interp>
